1
00:01:35,439 --> 00:01:38,400
Brother Ge, you're mistaken.

2
00:01:38,400 --> 00:01:41,480
The Yang family was removed from the Four Great Families.

3
00:01:41,480 --> 00:01:44,040
Now only my Lu family

4
00:01:45,280 --> 00:01:50,680
remains among the Mystic Medicine Association's Four Great Families.

5
00:01:51,040 --> 00:01:52,640
Medicine Master Lu is right.

6
00:02:01,200 --> 00:02:02,000
Lady Song.

7
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:08,360
The Mystic Water Hall has never changed its surname.

8
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:11,120
All of Mystic Water Hall welcomes the return of the Yang family's Young Master.

9
00:02:13,080 --> 00:02:14,240
You...

10
00:02:18,599 --> 00:02:20,080
Welcome back, Young Master.

11
00:02:31,280 --> 00:02:32,319
You people...

12
00:02:32,319 --> 00:02:33,280
What's going on with all of you?

13
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:43,759
What is this?

14
00:02:53,240 --> 00:02:55,080
All of Mystic Water Hall

15
00:02:55,080 --> 00:02:56,360
will give everything we have

16
00:02:56,360 --> 00:02:57,319
to support the Young Master,

17
00:02:57,319 --> 00:02:58,639
to win the Medicine Master title.

18
00:03:02,319 --> 00:03:04,680
Green Wood Hall will also fully assist the Young Master,

19
00:03:04,680 --> 00:03:06,599
to pass the final test and claim the title of Medicine Master,

20
00:03:06,599 --> 00:03:08,400
restoring the Traditionalist Faction's legitimacy.

21
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:08,919
Fine!

22
00:03:12,199 --> 00:03:12,919
So you've turned on me too!

23
00:03:19,360 --> 00:03:21,800
The Way of Healing is the foundation of the Mystic Medicine Association.

24
00:03:21,800 --> 00:03:24,319
Following ancestral rules is the proper path.

25
00:03:24,319 --> 00:03:26,840
We should indeed go by the rules.

26
00:03:26,840 --> 00:03:29,560
Only then can our Association's prestige shine.

27
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:32,759
Brother Yunfan, whether in character

28
00:03:32,759 --> 00:03:34,360
or in medical skill,

29
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:36,159
is of the highest caliber.

30
00:03:36,159 --> 00:03:39,680
For Uncle Yang and Uncle Ye to have a successor like you,

31
00:03:39,680 --> 00:03:43,120
ensures the Traditionalist Faction's name is not disgraced.

32
00:03:43,120 --> 00:03:44,080
At this time,

33
00:03:44,080 --> 00:03:45,639
my sister, Medicine Master Ge,

34
00:03:45,639 --> 00:03:48,560
couldn't attend due to ill health.

35
00:03:48,560 --> 00:03:51,639
But on her and Gilded Hall's behalf,

36
00:03:52,639 --> 00:03:55,199
I support Yang Yunfan's participation.

37
00:03:55,199 --> 00:03:56,479
Excellent!

38
00:03:57,400 --> 00:03:58,439
The Ge family is truly honorable!

39
00:03:58,439 --> 00:03:59,719
Yes, so honorable!

40
00:04:03,039 --> 00:04:03,840
What nonsense!

41
00:04:03,840 --> 00:04:05,319
Utter nonsense!

42
00:04:05,319 --> 00:04:06,599
What gives you the right to represent them?

43
00:04:06,599 --> 00:04:07,719
The Yang family is gone!

44
00:04:07,719 --> 00:04:08,319
Besides,

45
00:04:08,319 --> 00:04:10,319
Mystic Water Hall isn't the Yang family's private property.

46
00:04:10,319 --> 00:04:13,039
Mystic Water Hall has always honored the Yang family.

47
00:04:13,039 --> 00:04:14,879
Moreover, the late Medicine Master Yang

48
00:04:14,879 --> 00:04:16,839
had superb skills and a kind heart.

49
00:04:16,839 --> 00:04:19,040
He was the Association's youngest Medicine Prodigy.

50
00:04:19,040 --> 00:04:19,920
Don't forget,

51
00:04:19,920 --> 00:04:21,720
you're only an acting Medicine Master.

52
00:04:21,720 --> 00:04:22,800
You...

53
00:04:22,800 --> 00:04:23,480
This is mutiny!

54
00:04:23,480 --> 00:04:25,399
You've all rebelled against me!

55
00:04:25,399 --> 00:04:25,959
Medicine Master Li!

56
00:04:25,959 --> 00:04:27,360
Aren't you going to do something?

57
00:04:30,240 --> 00:04:32,279
I'm the chief examiner for the next round.

58
00:04:32,279 --> 00:04:33,240
I'll be on my way.

59
00:04:38,519 --> 00:04:39,279
Get back here with me, now!

60
00:04:40,319 --> 00:04:40,720
Medicine Master Li!

61
00:04:42,079 --> 00:04:43,199
What do we do now?

62
00:04:43,199 --> 00:04:44,680
No one saw this coming!

63
00:04:45,319 --> 00:04:47,319
Mystic Water Hall's Young Master Yang Yunfan!

64
00:04:47,759 --> 00:04:49,000
He looks really impressive.

65
00:04:49,879 --> 00:04:50,319
Everyone, please rise.

66
00:04:50,319 --> 00:04:51,160
Get up, please.

67
00:04:54,399 --> 00:04:58,439
Commanding an army feels amazing!

68
00:04:59,279 --> 00:05:00,399
Young Master.

69
00:05:00,399 --> 00:05:03,399
Don't forget, I can also give you massages.

70
00:05:04,879 --> 00:05:05,600
Lady Song,

71
00:05:05,600 --> 00:05:06,480
that won't be necessary.

72
00:05:06,480 --> 00:05:07,399
Qingxue, let's go, quickly.

73
00:05:08,920 --> 00:05:10,480
Farewell, Young Master.

74
00:05:10,480 --> 00:05:15,959
Good luck!

75
00:05:19,160 --> 00:05:20,319
Medicine Master Li.

76
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:21,720
Medicine Master Li, are we just letting him go?

77
00:05:21,720 --> 00:05:23,240
You're truly useless.

78
00:05:23,240 --> 00:05:24,399
After all these years,

79
00:05:24,399 --> 00:05:25,879
you can't even rein in the Yang family's old guard.

80
00:05:25,879 --> 00:05:26,680
And you're asking me?

81
00:05:26,680 --> 00:05:27,240
I...

82
00:05:28,079 --> 00:05:29,319
How have you been running things?

83
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:32,120
Medicine Master Li...

84
00:05:43,199 --> 00:05:44,199
For this round,

85
00:05:44,199 --> 00:05:45,680
first place Yang Yunfan

86
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:47,639
will pair with fourth place Lu Tanxiang.

87
00:05:51,560 --> 00:05:53,120
Second place Ye Qingxue

88
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:54,839
will pair with third place Li Xiangyang.

89
00:05:59,399 --> 00:06:00,040
Wait, what?

90
00:06:00,040 --> 00:06:00,800
On what grounds?

91
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:02,759
What kind of pairing is this?

92
00:06:02,759 --> 00:06:03,800
Li Mouren,

93
00:06:03,800 --> 00:06:04,879
just because your son is too weak,

94
00:06:04,879 --> 00:06:05,639
you can't deliberately target me!

95
00:06:05,639 --> 00:06:06,199
You...

96
00:06:08,800 --> 00:06:11,439
The examiner sets the rules for each round.

97
00:06:11,439 --> 00:06:12,560
Young Master Yang,

98
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:14,360
if you object, you may withdraw.

99
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:19,720
Since the examiner sets the rules,

100
00:06:21,319 --> 00:06:22,839
he must have his reasons.

101
00:06:24,360 --> 00:06:25,160
I have no objections.

102
00:06:33,240 --> 00:06:36,600
This round, you'll jointly treat this patient.

103
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:37,800
You will sequentially complete the three steps:

104
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:40,800
diagnosis, herb gathering, and treatment.

105
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:42,720
I will evaluate you based on treatment efficacy,

106
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:44,120
the rationality of your medication,

107
00:06:44,120 --> 00:06:46,720
and the accuracy of your herb gathering.

108
00:06:46,720 --> 00:06:48,040
Your overall scores will be ranked.

109
00:06:48,040 --> 00:06:50,040
The top two will advance.

110
00:06:50,040 --> 00:06:53,199
Distribute this round's herb-gathering maps.

111
00:06:56,720 --> 00:06:57,879
Yang Yunfan's group goes first.

112
00:07:11,839 --> 00:07:13,399
Extreme Yang Syndrome.

113
00:07:13,399 --> 00:07:14,600
Heat-toxin qi has invaded the body.

114
00:07:14,600 --> 00:07:15,240
Qi and blood flow in reverse.

115
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:16,720
This kind of illness

116
00:07:17,959 --> 00:07:18,560
is actually not too hard to treat.

117
00:07:19,240 --> 00:07:21,040
It is indeed Extreme Yang Syndrome,

118
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:22,560
but the herbs needed to treat it

119
00:07:22,560 --> 00:07:24,000
must come from regions of extreme yin.

120
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:24,920
They're rare and hard to find.

121
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:25,720
It won't be easy.

122
00:07:26,160 --> 00:07:26,759
Time's up.

123
00:07:31,000 --> 00:07:32,120
Li Xiangyang's group,

124
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:32,839
step forward and examine the patient.

125
00:07:43,519 --> 00:07:44,759
Take care of yourself.

126
00:07:44,759 --> 00:07:46,079
Don't worry, I'm tough to beat.

127
00:08:12,680 --> 00:08:13,759
Ye Qingxue,

128
00:08:13,759 --> 00:08:15,360
can you hurry up?

129
00:08:15,360 --> 00:08:16,480
We're here for an assessment,

130
00:08:16,480 --> 00:08:17,439
not for a leisurely stroll.

131
00:08:18,199 --> 00:08:20,199
This contest is timed, you know.

132
00:08:20,199 --> 00:08:22,600
I'm not like you Medicine Masters, climbing mountains daily for herbs,

133
00:08:22,600 --> 00:08:23,800
with your strong legs.

134
00:08:23,800 --> 00:08:25,399
I really can't walk anymore.

135
00:08:26,279 --> 00:08:27,000
I'm not moving.

136
00:08:27,959 --> 00:08:29,120
Don't be unreasonable.

137
00:08:29,120 --> 00:08:29,759
Get moving.

138
00:08:29,759 --> 00:08:30,600
No.

139
00:08:34,240 --> 00:08:35,159
If we're going, you carry me.

140
00:08:36,200 --> 00:08:37,600
What on earth do you want?

141
00:08:42,559 --> 00:08:43,480
Fine.

142
00:08:43,480 --> 00:08:44,639
Fine, come on.

143
00:08:44,639 --> 00:08:45,240
I'll carry you.

144
00:08:45,240 --> 00:08:46,200
Get on.

145
00:08:50,960 --> 00:08:52,200
Your clothes are dirty.

146
00:08:52,200 --> 00:08:52,960
I'm not getting on.

147
00:08:54,399 --> 00:08:56,399
Are you out of your mind, Ye Qingxue?

148
00:08:56,399 --> 00:08:58,440
Women and petty men are the hardest to deal with.

149
00:08:58,440 --> 00:08:59,120
You're not walking, huh?

150
00:08:59,120 --> 00:08:59,879
Worst case, we lose points.

151
00:08:59,879 --> 00:09:00,600
You...

152
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:02,639
Someone like you,

153
00:09:02,639 --> 00:09:04,320
what woman would ever let you provide for her?

154
00:09:04,320 --> 00:09:05,440
Disgusting.

155
00:09:30,159 --> 00:09:31,919
Wuming.

156
00:09:31,919 --> 00:09:34,120
Should we rest a bit before going in?

157
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:37,279
Why rest all of a sudden?

158
00:09:37,279 --> 00:09:39,279
Ghost Needle Grass only grows in damp, shaded places.

159
00:09:39,279 --> 00:09:40,879
If we don't make this quick,

160
00:09:40,879 --> 00:09:41,720
we'll run into trouble.

161
00:09:42,840 --> 00:09:43,840
Then let's hurry.

162
00:10:00,799 --> 00:10:02,519
Did you hear something?

163
00:10:07,840 --> 00:10:09,240
Don't tell me you're scared.

164
00:10:10,759 --> 00:10:11,879
No way.

165
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:16,000
A real man fears nothing in heaven or earth.

166
00:10:18,559 --> 00:10:19,320
There's nothing here.

167
00:10:19,320 --> 00:10:20,440
It's just the wind.

168
00:10:20,440 --> 00:10:21,320
There's nothing here.

169
00:10:21,320 --> 00:10:22,240
It's just the wind.

170
00:10:22,240 --> 00:10:23,399
A real man

171
00:10:23,399 --> 00:10:24,440
fears nothing in heaven or earth.

172
00:10:31,440 --> 00:10:31,879
What?

173
00:10:35,519 --> 00:10:35,960
We're done for!

174
00:10:38,120 --> 00:10:39,919
Black and White Impermanence!

175
00:10:39,919 --> 00:10:41,639
The same outfit scared you twice?

176
00:10:45,840 --> 00:10:47,360
Could we maybe not wear this outfit next time?

177
00:10:48,679 --> 00:10:49,399
Useless.

178
00:10:58,399 --> 00:10:59,519
Isn't that Li the Third?

179
00:11:00,279 --> 00:11:01,039
Looks like

180
00:11:01,039 --> 00:11:02,039
we're after the same thing.

181
00:11:02,840 --> 00:11:03,799
That's perfect.

182
00:11:04,559 --> 00:11:05,519
We can settle who's better.

183
00:11:06,919 --> 00:11:07,840
Goes without saying.

184
00:11:37,840 --> 00:11:39,960
What creepy act are you putting on now?

185
00:11:39,960 --> 00:11:41,480
Keep your voice down.

186
00:11:41,480 --> 00:11:42,759
Would it kill you to drop the act?

187
00:11:53,679 --> 00:11:55,240
Stop shaking. You're scared?

188
00:12:06,200 --> 00:12:06,879
Ghost Needle Grass.

189
00:12:09,039 --> 00:12:09,759
Are we in the wrong show?

190
00:12:09,759 --> 00:12:10,519
Is it this intense?

191
00:12:10,519 --> 00:12:11,440
Is this scene copyrighted?

192
00:12:11,440 --> 00:12:11,919
Shouldn't it be censored?

193
00:12:11,919 --> 00:12:12,559
Stop joking around.

194
00:12:13,000 --> 00:12:14,279
Once Ghost Needle Grass hits the ground,

195
00:12:14,279 --> 00:12:15,519
its needles close up and can't be picked.

196
00:12:15,519 --> 00:12:16,000
Hurry and pick it now.

197
00:12:16,879 --> 00:12:17,759
Do we really have to pick it?

198
00:12:17,759 --> 00:12:19,320
I think this damp, gloomy place of your Mystic Medicine Association

199
00:12:19,320 --> 00:12:20,759
should have a "no visitors" sign, right?

200
00:12:26,039 --> 00:12:27,279
That cool, huh?

201
00:12:34,960 --> 00:12:35,519
What the heck?

202
00:12:37,799 --> 00:12:38,440
That actually works?

203
00:12:40,399 --> 00:12:41,480
Impressive!

204
00:12:43,799 --> 00:12:44,399
Awesome.

205
00:12:45,559 --> 00:12:46,000
Way to go!

206
00:12:47,000 --> 00:12:49,559
No one can stop me in this competition.

207
00:12:49,559 --> 00:12:50,600
Green Wood Hall,

208
00:12:51,440 --> 00:12:52,480
I'm claiming it.

209
00:12:55,600 --> 00:12:56,240
Trying to slip away?

210
00:12:56,960 --> 00:12:57,399
I'll fight you to the end!

211
00:13:05,559 --> 00:13:06,919
Qingxue.

212
00:13:06,919 --> 00:13:08,399
Look at those people.

213
00:13:08,399 --> 00:13:10,279
They look just like the long-dead patients buried by your family.

214
00:13:14,919 --> 00:13:17,080
These patients really are strange.

215
00:13:17,080 --> 00:13:20,200
Their aura does resemble our Ye family's technique,

216
00:13:20,200 --> 00:13:22,200
but they're mixed with something else.

217
00:13:22,200 --> 00:13:24,480
I think they are being controlled.

218
00:13:28,360 --> 00:13:29,039
Li Xiangyang.

219
00:13:30,320 --> 00:13:32,519
In a team match, you didn't bring your teammate?

220
00:13:32,519 --> 00:13:33,159
Want to lose points?

221
00:13:40,159 --> 00:13:42,360
If my teammate is gone,

222
00:13:42,360 --> 00:13:43,320
then there's no need.
